CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper January 25, 1947, pg. 19, reads: "December Bride and Groom - Mrs. Della Tyler of 120 Trent Street was married Dec. 21 to Jesse Brown by the Rev. J. J. Green. A delightful reception followed the ceremony at the home of the reverent. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Della Tyler wearing fox stole, and Jesse Brown standing in front of light colored background with dark curtains in Harris Studio
